summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending page 24-396 of the Seattle Municipal Code (Plat 73W, Page 173 of the official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300) to rezone certain property located on the west side of Empire Way South between South Graham Street and South Morgan Street from Single Family Residence High Density (RS 5000) and Community Business (BC) to General Commercial (CG) and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith (Petition of U-Haul Company of Western Washington) (C.F. 290617).
